ADDITIONAL SECURITY DISCLAIMER:

This software modifies DNS infrastructure and should only be used with proper
authorization. The authors and contributors assume no liability for misuse,
unauthorized DNS modifications, or any damages resulting from the use of this
software.

IMPORTANT WARNINGS:
1. Demo credentials are included for testing - MUST be changed for any real use
2. Simplified cryptography is used - replace with bcrypt/Argon2 for production
3. DNS UPDATE functionality is partially implemented - complete before production
4. This tool is intended for authorized security research, honeypot deployment,
   and educational purposes only

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK. Always obtain proper authorization before modifying
DNS infrastructure.
